<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag 'profile.png', alt: 'profile image', class: 'profile-img' %>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>As a new developer, I have devoured information and training from every resource possible. I've worked alongside junior- and mid-level developers and have built my own projects (which you can find in my portfolio).</p>

        <p>I strive for excellence in both form and functionality, and work hard to deliver a product that satisfies client's needs and desires, delivered on time and on budget.</p>

        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block job">
              Job 1
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block job">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block job">
              School 1
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block job">
              School 2
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block job">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>